<h2><a id=3D"sensitive-events" name=3D"sensitive-events"></a>Sensitive even=
ts</h2>

<div class=3D"no-margin"><div class=3D"no-margin">
  <p>A "Sensitive Event" is an unforeseen event or development that creates=
 significant risk to Google's ability to provide high quality, relevant inf=
ormation and ground truth, and reduce insensitive or exploitative content i=
n prominent and monetized features<strong>.</strong> During a sensitive eve=
nt, we may take a variety of actions to address these risks.</p>
</div>
</div>

